1
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:09,649
On the basis of the statements
of Saraswati Thakur ...

2
00:00:11,513 --> 00:00:17,363
We're saying that as the physical

3
00:00:17,394 --> 00:00:21,963
the subtle and gross bodies
are the outcome of exploiting tendency,

4
00:00:21,963 --> 00:00:28,333
the swarup, or the spiritual body,
is comprised of dedicating tendency

5
00:00:28,333 --> 00:00:30,849
of devotional tendencies.

6
00:00:35,598 --> 00:00:42,108
Srila Guru Maharaj mentions
the concept of roochie-puriksha

7
00:00:42,871 --> 00:00:47,481
which means where the guru
is examining the roochie

8
00:00:47,481 --> 00:00:51,724
the taste of his disciple
as Saraswati Thakur did to him

9
00:00:53,613 --> 00:00:55,006
when they come to Cadam Cundy

10
00:00:56,006 --> 00:00:59,603
And Saraswati Thakur says
"which place do you like best?"

11
00:00:59,603 --> 00:01:01,184
he said: "Cadam Cundy"

12
00:01:01,696 --> 00:01:05,696
then, some years later,
the party, again, they run tour

13
00:01:05,696 --> 00:01:08,409
and they come to Cadam Cundy
and Saraswati Thakur says:

14
00:01:08,409 --> 00:01:14,459
"your place?" And Guru Maharaj
realizes: oh, he's examining the taste

15
00:01:14,459 --> 00:01:18,360
and spiritual tendency.

16
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:24,587
So, when ... says: ...

17
00:01:27,474 --> 00:01:29,734
He signs at the sweeper.

18
00:01:33,094 --> 00:01:35,624
Srila Saraswati Thakur said:

19
00:01:35,624 --> 00:01:40,413
"If ... is the sweeper
in that divine domain,

20
00:01:40,413 --> 00:01:44,996
then I'm one straws in his broom.

21
00:01:45,005 --> 00:01:48,715
And Srila Guru Maharaj made
this observation. He said,

22
00:01:48,715 --> 00:01:53,425
if we take this as a sincere
expression, which we do,

23
00:01:55,425 --> 00:02:01,445
he said, then you can understand
the unit of construction of the swarup,

24
00:02:01,448 --> 00:02:04,278
of the spiritual body.

25
00:02:04,278 --> 00:02:10,574
So, what we take away from this,
as with dedicating tendencies,

26
00:02:12,751 --> 00:02:18,821
the exploiting tendencies
are minimized and diminishing,

27
00:02:18,821 --> 00:02:23,623
and those which are sustaining
the mundane form,

28
00:02:23,623 --> 00:02:29,294
that means that gradually the layers,
karma and ..., they're vanishing.

29
00:02:29,294 --> 00:02:32,203
As in the roochie-puriksha,
Guru Maharaj said,

30
00:02:32,203 --> 00:02:38,254
the guru, in this case Saraswati Thakur,
he's beginning to see the swarup

31
00:02:38,254 --> 00:02:42,174
manifest on account
of dedicating tendencies.

